# REST Client testing file untuk Auth Module API
# Gunakan ekstensi REST Client di VS Code atau jalankan curl manual.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### 1. Register Guru Baru
# @name registerTeacher
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Guru Budi Baru",
  "email": "budibaru@school.com",
  "password": "secretpassword",
  "role": "teacher",
  "avatar": "https://avatar.iran.liara.run/public/teacher"
}

### 2. Login Guru yang Baru Didaftarkan
# @name loginTeacher
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "budibaru@school.com",
  "password": "secretpassword"
}

### Salin token hasil login di atas dan letakkan di variabel token di bawah ini:
@token = {{loginTeacher.response.body.access_token}}

### 3. Mengambil Profil Saya (/me) menggunakan Token JWT
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Login Akun Seed (Guru Budi bawaan seeding database)
# Karena seeding.py sudah diupdate menggunakan password hashing,
# user default "teacher@school.com" dengan password "password123" bisa langsung login.
# @name loginSeed
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher@school.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 5. Mengambil Profil Saya (/me) Akun Seed
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSeed.response.body.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
